{"id":24255,"title":"Clinical evaluation of vancomycin dosage in pediatric oncology patients.","abstract":"Vancomycin trough serum concentrations were below therapeutic range (8-15 mg/L) in 58% of 124 pediatric oncology patients receiving 60 mg/kg/d divided qid. Patients <6 and between 6 and 12 years had significantly lower trough concentrations than patients >12 years. A vancomycin dosage of 60 mg/kg/d is inadequate for pediatric oncology patients >12 years. ","date":"2014-06-12","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24445830","annotations":[{"name":"Blood plasma","weight":0.833965,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood_plasma"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.797998,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Dose (biochemistry)","weight":0.753863,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dose_(biochemistry)"},{"name":"Pediatrics","weight":0.75303,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pediatrics"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.704197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Oncology","weight":0.696813,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oncology"},{"name":"Therapeutic index","weight":0.662441,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapeutic_index"},{"name":"Vancomycin","weight":0.176389,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vancomycin"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"815","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/815"},{"name":"Evaluation","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evaluation"},{"name":"Trough (meteorology)","weight":0.013127,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trough_(meteorology)"}]}
